{"author":"Joe Oakhart","author_email":"joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com","author_id":"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d","author_sig":"{\"payload\": \"\", \"payloadType\": \"application/vnd.rebar.authorship.v1+json\", \"signatures\": [{\"keyid\": \"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d\", \"sig\": \"\"}]}","data":{"body":"Eighth remediation: replaced all competing identity descriptions with one canonical four-field, length-prefixed prerequisite encoding; explicitly preserved the legacy pipe-delimited encoding for all non-prerequisite findings. Also documented reuse of the existing runner retry policy, structured indeterminate observability, and the parent-contract rationale for the plan-review-only optional verifier field."},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"COMMENT","timestamp":1784567571553590001,"uuid":"72da444a-7237-4e47-91c1-20619ead263c"}